msg: Refactored to remove a lot of code relating SharedData and Participants directly to Widgets and WidgetInstances and replaced with a single "SharedDataHelper" service facade to manage all access to shared data - this means we consistently manage the relationship via the internal shared data key which is constructed in a single way.
